      • postcodeToPoints

        public static TreeMap<String,uk.ac.leeds.ccg.andyt.agdtgeotools.AGDT_Point> postcodeToPoints(TreeMap<String,String> input,
                                                                                             String yM3v)
        Parameters:
        input - TreeMap where values are postcodes for which the coordinates are to be returned as a AGDT_Point.
        yM3v -
        Returns:
        TreeMap with the keys as in input and values calculated using getPointFromPostcode(value). If no look up is found for a postcode its key does not get put into the result.
